== Why 2nd ? ==

The name of the article is '''Çandarlı (2nd) Halil Pasha''' . Why ? The article of the first Çandarlı Halil Pasha is [[Çandarlı Kara Halil Hayreddin Pasha]]. So there is no risk of confusing the names. [[User:Nedim Ardoğa|Nedim Ardoğa]] ([[User talk:Nedim Ardoğa|talk]]) 13:05, 2 November 2009 (UTC)

